ion He has given us of Himself -- the Bible. We place great emphasis on the teaching of the Bible to learn who He is and how He desires to be worshipped.</p>\n<p>We Believe the worship of God should be spiritual. Therefore: We choose to be flexible and yield our lives to the direction of the Holy Spirit.</p>\n<p>We Believe the worship of God should be inspirational. Therefore: We give great place to music in our worship.</p>\n<p>We Believe the worship of God should be fruitful. Therefore: We look for His love in our lives as evidence that we have been truly worshipping Him.</p>\n<p>We Believe God desires to extend His love to all. Therefore: We welcome all to come and join us as we seek to worship Him in unity.</p>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}}}',0,1308974844,1),('field:node:20','a:1:{s:4:\"body\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:\"value\";s:81:\"Community bulletin board. Probably the Google Spreadsheets widget we usually use?\";s:7:\"summary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:13:\"filtered_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";s:89:\"<p>Community bulletin board. Probably the Google Spreadsheets widget we usually use?</p>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}}}',0,1308973633,1),('field:node:21','a:1:{s:4:\"body\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:\"value\";s:20:\"List of home groups.\";s:7:\"summary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:13:\"filtered_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";s:28:\"<p>List of home groups.</p>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}}}',0,1308973684,1),('field:node:22','a:1:{s:4:\"body\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:\"value\";s:13:\"HG info here.\";s:7:\"summary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:13:\"filtered_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";s:21:\"<p>HG info here.</p>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}}}',0,1308973720,1),('field:node:23','a:1:{s:4:\"body\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:\"value\";s:13:\"HG info here.\";s:7:\"summary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:13:\"filtered_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";s:21:\"<p>HG info here.</p>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}